1. Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/find-a-fixed-point-in-a-given-array/
Question : Find a Fixed Point (Value equal to index) in a given array
Answer: 1. In sorted distinct array the difference between the i-a[i] will be a non decreasing function
        .So use a binary search to find the fixed point where i-a[i]==0
        
